{"tid":88173,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"兩句","createTime":"2017-01-20T12:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T17:10:28.000Z","uid":27741,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bf51622b13ffae78b3869e00544d5a34adcc9e3d","tid":88173,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:06:59.000Z","msg":"I met the the most beautiful woman today. She said we have been married for 34 years.<br />\n今天我遇上個最美麗的女人。她說我們已結婚三十四載。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThey told me they could save either my wife or my son.<br />\nThey were wrong.<br />\n他們說會救活我妻兒其中一個。他們錯了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHe never wanted to leave his wife<br />\nBut it was getting late and the graveyard gates were about to be closed.<br />\n他一直沒想過要離開他的妻子。奈何墓園因天色已晚快要關閉了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI found the love of my life. She didnt.<br />\n我找到了一生最愛。她沒有。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThree months ago, he gave me a ring. Two days ago, the Army gave me a flag.<br />\n三個月前，他給了我一隻戒指。兩天前，軍隊給了我一支旗。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nI jumped. Then I regretted it.<br />\n我跳了。然後我後悔了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔翻譯下面依啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe&rsquo;re lying in bed. She&rsquo;s lying.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBrought roses home. Keys didn't fit.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nShe found him hanging. She followed.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThere're two voices in our bedroom. I knock.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFailed class and attempted suicide. Failed again.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSmoking my very last cigarette. Again.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Wax wings, high hopes. Long fall. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"f0db1857c6c7a02e27631784d51cfc21edef1e4e","tid":88173,"uid":47463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:16:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Failed class and attempted suicide. Failed again.</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"263c3c0d81ce7b02ca91e73e870dde3963ef8287","tid":88173,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:33:34.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9015b17a22345f9dce22ca5aee40a160a669f89f","tid":88173,"uid":15960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:38:28.000Z","msg":"好正"},{"pid":"2054469ebe55119070d901712d8cf6156549f47b","tid":88173,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 巴打你好"},{"pid":"745468751fc3d285c88f5bec16764e71264f95ea","tid":88173,"uid":37348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf467a75c05ec5c7fc297e714710315244f6ac44","tid":88173,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到你真係好"},{"pid":"b03826845ae0091e8c1ad74d05083b8c1238a913","tid":88173,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T13:00:12.000Z","msg":"&quot;I'll be back tomorrow.&quot; Years ago.<br />\n多年前他話明天會回來。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWrong number. Said by a familiar voice.<br />\n號碼錯了。一把熟悉的聲音說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHe loved cigarettes... More than life.<br />\n他愛香煙...比生命更甚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTurn me off. First thing said by the first sentient robot.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHer baby has Jame's eyes. And John's surname.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFound true love. Married someone else."},{"pid":"00117c4fdce1739dad4066631ab47ef326db56da","tid":88173,"uid":27741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T14:27:57.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"812b7845